design function, including \code{check_treatments}, \code{check_families}, \code{n_blocks},
\code{n_rows}, \code{n_cols}, \code{cluster_source}, and any other argument accepted by the
respective function.

For \code{alpha_rc_stream()} environments, \code{entry_treatments} and
\code{entry_families} are set internally from the allocation result and must not
